<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Job Recommendation</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: white;
            color: #333;
            min-height: 100vh; /* Ensure full viewport height */
            position: relative; /* Needed for footer positioning */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 60px; /* Adjusted for footer space */
        }

        /* Navbar Styles */
        .navbar {
            background-color: #AF8F6F;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .navbar-nav {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar-nav li {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .navbar-nav li:first-child {
            margin-left: 0;
        }

        .navbar-nav li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Main Content Styles */
        h1, h2 {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            color: #AD7B54;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-family: fantasy;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #fff;
            background-image: url("i4.jpg");
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 70px auto;
            max-width: 1000px;
            height: 400px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .card-input {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background-color: rgba(235, 232, 232, 0.635);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(91, 91, 91, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 400px;
            max-height: 200px;
            width: calc(100% - 80px);
            height: calc(100% - 80px);
        }

        label {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        button[type="submit"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #AF8F6F;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        button[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #815931; /* Adjusted to match user's preferred color */
        }

        /* Recommendation Cards Styles */
        .recommendation-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .recommendation-card {
            width: calc(50% - 20px); /* Adjusted to cover half of the screen */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 20px); /* Added flex properties for responsive design */
            max-width: calc(50% - 20px); /* Added max-width for responsiveness */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-height: 200px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .recommendation-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .textbox-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        textarea {
    width: 70%;
    height: 700px; /* Adjust height as needed */
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    resize: none; /* Disable resizing */
    overflow-y: auto; /* Enable vertical scroll if content exceeds */
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; /* Match body font */
    font-size: 1rem; /* Match paragraph font size */
    text-align: left; /* Adjust text alignment */
    box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Increased intensity for normal state */
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease; /* Smooth transition for box-shadow */
}

textarea:focus {
    outline: none; /* Remove default focus outline */
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); /* Intensified shadow on focus */
}


        /* Footer Styles */
        .footer {
            background-color: #AF8F6F; /* Match navbar background color */
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-brand">CAREER CATALYST</div>
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i> Trending News</a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Reviews</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Don't be pushed around by the fears in your mind.<br>Be led by the dreams in your heart.</h1>
        <p>Explore Your Interests: Begin your career journey by exploring your interests, hobbies, and passions.<br>Consider what activities bring you joy and fulfillment. Your interests can provide valuable insights into potential career paths.</p>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-input">
                <form id="job-finder" action="/career" method="post">
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <label for="c_education">Education</label>
                        <input type="text" id="c_education" name="c_education" required><br>
                        <label for="Details">Interests</label>
                        <input type="text" id="Details" name="Details" required><br>
                        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Your Exclusive Suggestions</h2>
        <% if (locals.result) { %>
            <div class="textbox-container">
                <textarea id="recommendation-textbox" rows="30" readonly placeholder="Enter your exclusive suggestions..."><%= result %></textarea>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Career Catalyst. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
